{"tid":275452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【彈劾689】陳克勤：如特首有問題中央會唔查？如斷正佢走得甩咩？","createTime":"2017-06-08T04:52:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T05:18:36.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5494c3b99f2b64ccf7eefa18382626384ad706e2","tid":275452,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:52:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170608/large/1496896232_57be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170608%2Flarge%2F1496896232_57be.jpg&h=9c0af780&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特首梁振英私通民建聯周浩鼎，修改立法會調查UGL事宜專責委員會文件，被轟公然干預立法會，令調查對自己有利。28名民主派議員將在昨日在立法會大會引用《基本法》73（9）條啟動彈劾特首梁振英的議案，議案由公民黨黨魁楊岳橋動議。立法會早上復會，各議員繼續就議案發言。《蘋果》全程直播 <a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/livestream/channel/legco\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Flivestream%2Fchannel%2Flegco&d=Cw2PUvMBpwLuQPtG7jJqAjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=e407d318\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Flivestream%2Fchannel%2Flegco&h=b51f8f7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/livestream/channel/legco</a> 。<br />\n<br />\n周浩鼎黨友、民建聯副主席陳克勤發言時指，梁振英餘下任期不足三個星期，認為毋須浪費議會時間，試圖對梁振英作出彈劾。他又認為彈劾是茲事體大，不應隨意提出，批評泛民濫用提出彈劾議案的權力。<br />\n<br />\n陳克勤又指，梁振英即使升任國家領導人，若果犯法，逃不過中央追究，「連國家軍委副主席都因為貪腐而被起訴，更何況是區區一個行政長官，如果佢有問題，中央政府會唔查咩？會翹埋對手咩？如果佢斷正，佢會走得甩咩？」<br />\n商界廖長江則批評，民主派以要留下紀錄，作為彈劾梁振英的理據，是自欺欺人，輕視基本法賦予立法會職能的嚴肅性，令彈劾權淪為民主派製造歷史的政治工具。民建聯陳克勤斥民主派「疑心生暗鬼」，認為議案無聊兼浪費會議時間。<br />\n工聯會立法會議員何啟明認為，梁振英透過周浩鼎表達修改調查範圍的意見，只是交流意見，並非違法，只是「議會政治」一部分：「好似平時立法會審議工程，政府先會畀一啲基本資料我哋，等我哋對工程有更加多嘅了解，然後我哋議會發言，係提昇議會效率。」"},{"pid":"ee85de28839317316186cb05c096b882f8ac91ad","tid":275452,"uid":997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:53:54.000Z","msg":"共產黨係法律上有咩能力叫特首躝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n民建聯d狗真係諗住講100次大話就係真"},{"pid":"43ab82811c8de993a5f9bdc8280b1ea1396b498a","tid":275452,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:56:54.000Z","msg":"倒果為因<br />\n你唔查又點會走唔甩<br />\n支共查唔杳關我咩事<br />\n香港特首梗係香港查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e46ca990bdebc0be3e3cc332d7ec9c961092551","tid":275452,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:58:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e86ca47ddbea6cdc97f7833a61103b1e3b41a421","tid":275452,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:02:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>倒果為因<br />\n你唔查又點會走唔甩<br />\n支共查唔杳關我咩事<br />\n香港特首梗係香港查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n四眼仔破壞中國兩制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd5d1df401e32f3b0a3bb2ce28a305228c342db","tid":275452,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:18:36.000Z","msg":"豬隊友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}